EXTRACTED VALUE: "I know that." It was my birthday, too, and I wasn't going to spend it with Trent. Ticked, I headed into the kitchen after Ivy.
"Wait here now for me. I go ahead to warn them. You do not want to be shot at carrying that stuff."
"We will be burned alive!" Madilla, her servant, screamed behind her. "Run! Run and hide!"
Nathanael Greene felt certain that Washington only needed time to make himself "acquainted with the genius" of the New England troops.
